abstract: OLD WESTBURY, L.I., Aug. 29--Peggy Kass of Jumping Brook and Dave Elkind of Hollywood scored 40, 39--79 and won the Women's Metropolitan Golf Association junior girls mixed-foursome tournament today on a draw at the Old Westbury Golf and Country Club. Par for the 6,432-yard course is 36, 36--72.
